			<Condition><![CDATA[Updating AND (DFLT_FL = true) AND (:Old.DFLT_FL = false)]]></Condition>
			<Description><![CDATA[When a record is updated, only one record can be set as the default record.  Therefore, if this record's DFLT_FL is now true but was false, then the existing default record needs to be updated to set its DFLT_FL to false.  Note that constraint DfltFlUpdating handles the reverse situation.]]></Description>
